SOURCEDETAIL: The data are generally obtained on an activity level, and include numerous parameters. They can thus be disaggregated by provider and recipient country by type of finance, and by type of resources provided. Some data are also available on the policy objectives targeted by individual projects.
FOOTNOTES: Data for 2005 refer to 2002 to 2005 period.
